{"tid":928420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"問答網Quora遭入侵 近億用戶信息外泄","createTime":"2018-12-04T22:27:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T01:05:31.000Z","uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"82fa32a5890463c5925782446a595eec44df9d60","tid":928420,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T22:27:15.000Z","msg":"【大公報訊】據路透社及TechCrunch網站報道：繼連鎖酒店萬豪國際集團五億帳號被盜後，線上問答網站Quora4日表示，該網站伺服器受到「惡意第三方」的非法入侵，約有一億用戶的信息可能因此泄露。<br />\n<br />\n　　Quora表示，公司是於上周五發現被入侵，受泄露的用戶信息包括姓名、郵箱地址和密碼，有些入侵與該公司使用的支付交易服務網站Stripe有關。Quora已強制把所有受影響帳戶登出，避免造成進一步的損失。<br />\n<br />\n　　公司行政總裁丹吉洛（Adam D&lsquo;Angelo）在刊登聲明表示：「我們已經告知執法部門，同時正在通知信息被泄露的用戶，要求他們更改登入方法。」不過，他強調，外泄資料不含信用卡或身份證號碼等敏感內容，故用戶身份被盜用機會很低，且匿名發起或回答問題的用戶未受影響。<br />\n<br />\n　　Quora網站於2009年由丹吉洛和奇弗（Charlie Cheever）創辦，兩位都是前Facebook員工。用戶通常透過平台互相提問、解答宗教、政治，以至兩性關係等問題。2015年Quora報稱全球每月有兩億個帳戶登錄使用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.takungpao.com.hk/news/232111/2018/1205/215319.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takungpao.com.hk%2Fnews%2F232111%2F2018%2F1205%2F215319.html&d=1sVcEiuYA9%2FCtHdq16%2FHB26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=e6a77263\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.takungpao.com.hk/news/232111/2018/1205/215319.html</a>"},{"pid":"a9c514441f95f9c8202963fd36eec88eca1fc154","tid":928420,"uid":104767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T00:32:08.000Z","msg":"本身已經係左膠同五毛聚腳之地"},{"pid":"e35ea1fa50254002f7230d7588796d741378ef64","tid":928420,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a9c514441f95f9c8202963fd36eec88eca1fc154","tid":928420,"uid":104767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T00:32:08.000Z","msg":"本身已經係左膠同五毛聚腳之地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T01:03:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">淪陷咗好耐</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/4e/Wiki-black.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F4%2F4e%2FWiki-black.png&h=17e6601f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c53a84186564099a835aa8c6b8b93ba61b4ee882","tid":928420,"uid":28195,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a9c514441f95f9c8202963fd36eec88eca1fc154","tid":928420,"uid":104767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T00:32:08.000Z","msg":"本身已經係左膠同五毛聚腳之地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T01:05:31.000Z","msg":"Quora 好撚多英語5毛，痴撚線"}]}